title: Giulio Gallarotti: Tennis Trash
description: Comedian Giulio Gallarotti joins us this week on AYG. Giulio tells us about getting a tattoo from his friend Pete Davidson, wearing Ed Hardy shirts, and his purple Volkswagen.  You may know Giulo Gallarotti from touring with Pete Davidson, appearance on Ramy, or MTV, SUBSCRIBE. RATE. REVIEW.
